OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine and
OL,6,Fdry evening for much of the region
OL,7,Fwith some sunny intervals. Patchy
OL,8,Fcloud becomes widespread from the east
OL,9,Fovernight but expected to remain dry.
OL,10,FLight northerly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FAn increasingly cloudy start
OL,13,Fto the day, with patchy drizzle
OL,14,Fpossible. Greater potential for sunny
OL,15,Fintervals in the afternoon and
OL,16,Fevening. Light northerly winds,
OL,17,Flocally stronger along coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
